# GRAPHICS::GET_STATUS_OF_TAKE_HIGH_QUALITY_PHOTO

## Summary
Call this after calling BEGIN_TAKE_HIGH_QUALITY_PHOTO to check when the operation has finished, and whether it succeeded

## Returns
* **PHOTO_OPERATION_STATUS**
